    <ProjectSection>
      <CopiesWrapper>
        <h1>What's next?</h1>
        <p>In December 2022, our work stopped due to company restructuring, leading to team layoffs. The design system is an ongoing project, and we have essential components ready for easy adoption by any future team.</p>
        <p>Creating a design system may initially seem time and cost-intensive, but the long-term benefits include saving time and money by avoiding redundant work and allowing teams to focus on more important tasks.</p>
      </CopiesWrapper>
      <CopiesWrapper>
        <h2>Reflection</h2>
        <p>It was an 'Everest' challenge. I learned much about resource management, coordinating moving parts, and syncing with developers. I am proud I convinced management to give the design system initiative a well-deserved try.</p>
      </CopiesWrapper>
    </ProjectSection>
  </main>
